OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out millions after
OL,4,C'serious' sewage network breaches
OL,6,FDwr Cymru Welsh Water will pay out
OL,7,F#44.7 million for "serious" breaches
OL,8,Fin its sewage and network services and
OL,9,Fmust now focus on "putting things
OL,10,Fright", regulator Ofwat has announced.
OL,12,FThe water watchdog said it had
OL,13,Faccepted the supplier's settlement
OL,14,Fpackage, which was first proposed in
OL,15,FMarch, following consultation.
OL,26,@nD@Bs{oD@SOUoD@[O]qD@SOUrD@FO]
