PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780916574
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out millions after
OL,4,C'serious' sewage network breaches
OL,6,FOfwat said the supplier failed to
OL,7,Fproperly operate, maintain and upgrade
OL,8,Fits wastewater network to ensure it
OL,9,Fcould cope with levels of sewage and
OL,10,Fwastewater, and did not have adequate
OL,11,Fprocesses in place or oversight by
OL,12,Fsenior bosses.
OL,14,FThe enforcement package will include
OL,15,F#40.6 million to reduce spills at
OL,16,Fspecific overflows and reduce the
OL,17,Fenvironmental damage caused, tackle
OL,18,Fgroundwater entering the sewer
OL,19,Fnetwork, as well as an extra #4.1
OL,20,Fmillion to improve river quality in
OL,21,F"extremely sensitive catchments".
OL,26,@}D@AOU}D@`O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/10
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
