OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780916574
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out millions after
OL,4,C'serious' sewage network breaches
OL,6,FLynn Parker, senior director for
OL,7,Fenforcement at Ofwat, said: "Our
OL,8,Finvestigation found serious and
OL,9,Funacceptable breaches in how Dwr Cymru
OL,10,FWelsh Water has operated its
OL,11,Fwastewater assets which has resulted
OL,12,Fin excessive spills to the environment.
OL,14,F"With this investigation now
OL,15,Fconcluded, we expect the company to
OL,16,Ffocus on putting things right so that
OL,17,Fcustomers can regain trust in their
OL,18,Fwater company."
OL,26,@oD@]OUvD@AOUzD@OO]
