OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780916574
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out millions after
OL,4,C'serious' sewage network breaches
OL,6,F"The investigation considered both
OL,7,Fhistoric and more recent compliance,
OL,8,Fand we recognise that improvements are
OL,9,Fneeded. Over the past year, we have
OL,10,Falready begun a major transformation
OL,11,Fprogramme across the business,
OL,12,Fincluding our wastewater services,
OL,13,Ffocused on improving governance,
OL,14,Fstrengthening operational oversight,
OL,15,Faccelerating investment and delivering
OL,16,Fbetter outcomes for customers and the
OL,17,Fenvironment.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/10
