OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780916574
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out millions after
OL,4,C'serious' sewage network breaches
OL,6,F"While we know there is much more to
OL,7,Fdo and that it will take time to get
OL,8,Fto the level of performance our
OL,9,Fcustomers and regulators rightly
OL,10,Fexpect, we are beginning to see early
OL,11,Fsigns of progress in some key areas of
OL,12,Fperformance. During 2025/26, leakage
OL,13,Fhas started to reduce following
OL,14,Fincreased repair activity and
OL,15,Fprogressive metering, customer
OL,16,Fcomplaints relating to water quality
OL,17,Fhave reduced following targeted work
OL,18,Fon our network, and incidents of
OL,19,Finternal sewer flooding have reduced.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/10
