PN,46708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780916574
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out millions after
OL,4,C'serious' sewage network breaches
OL,6,FThe statement continued: "As part of
OL,7,Fthis package, #42 million will be
OL,8,Finvested in reducing spills from
OL,9,Fspecific storm overflows and tackling
OL,10,Fgroundwater entering the sewer network
OL,11,F` a major contributor to frequent
OL,12,Fspills. This will include targeted
OL,13,Finvestment at priority sites,
OL,14,Falongside investigations and
OL,15,Fimprovement work to reduce
OL,16,Finfiltration across parts of the
OL,17,Fnetwork.
OL,26,@nD@ZOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/10
