OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1780916574
OL,3,CWelsh Water to pay out millions after
OL,4,C'serious' sewage network breaches
OL,6,F"A further #2 million will support
OL,7,Fimprovements to river habitats, while
OL,8,Fa new #1 million Cymuned Natur Fund
OL,9,Fwill provide practical support to
OL,10,Fcommunity groups and charities working
OL,11,Fto protect and enhance the environment
OL,12,Facross Wales.
OL,14,F"These commitments are additional to
OL,15,Four #4.2 billion investment programme
OL,16,Ffor 2025`2030, including #2.5 billion
OL,17,Fdedicated to environmental
OL,18,Fimprovements and #889 million
OL,19,Fspecifically targeted at improving
OL,20,Fstorm overflows.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/10
